Akoum
Oracle: Players may cast enchantment cards as though they had flash.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, destroy target creature that isn't enchanted


Aretopolis
Oracle: When you planeswalk to Aretopolis or at the beginning of your upkeep, put a scroll counter on Aretopolis, then you gain life equal to the number of scroll counters on it.\n When Aretopolis has ten or more scroll counters on it, planeswalk.
Chaos: Whenevre you roll <Chaos>, put a scroll counter on Aretopolis, then draw cards equal to the number of scroll counters on it.


Astral_Arena
Oracle: No more than one creature can ttack each combat.\n No more than one creatre can block each combat.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, Astral Arena deals 2 damage to each creature.

Bloodhill_Bastion
Oracle: Whenever a creature enters the battlefield, it gains double strike and haste until end of turn.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, exile target nontoken creature you control, then return it to the battlefield under your control.

Edge_of_Malacol
Oracle: If a creature you control would untap during your untap step, put two +1/+1 counters on it instead.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, untap each creature you control.

Furnace_Layer
Oracle: When you planeswalk to Furnace layer of at the beginnig of your upkeep, select target player at random. That player discards a card. If that player discards a land card this way, s/he loses 3 life.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, you may destroy target nonland permanent

Gavony
Oracle: All creatures have vigilance.
Chaos: Whenever you roll <Chaos>, creatures you control are indestructible this turn.

Glen_Elendra
Oracle: At end of combat, you may exchange control of target creature you control that dealt combat damage to a player this combat and target creature that player controls
Chaos: ... gain control of target creature you own.

Grand_Ossuary
Oracle: Whenever a creature dies, its controller distributes a number of +1/+1 coutners equal to its power among any number of target creatues s/he controls. 
Chaos: ..., each player exiles all creatures s/he controls and pus X 1/1 green Saprling creature tokens onto the battlefield, where X is the total power of all creatures s/he exiled this way. Then planeswalk away.
